Date: Fri, 27 Aug 1999 17:51:53 -0600 (CST)
From: "Julie Rawlings" <Julie.Rawlings@tdh.state.tx.us>

The official dengue count in Webb County (Laredo is in Webb County) to date
is 5 cases -- 4 in patients who had traveled to Nuevo Laredo [Mexico and
one in a patient who denies travel in the 2 weeks prior to onset of illness.
Several suspect cases are under investigation.
Any new predictions? [See [03 below - Mod.JW
